description: Fathead is a new start-up BBQ truck serving the best pork and chicken BBQ in central Arkansas! With the most amazing southern fried catfish, hand cut and breaded chicken tenders, and real hand cut fries on the menu as well, there's no way you can go wrong. Looking for a side to round out your meal? Try the traditional homemade sides like cole slaw, potato salad, baked beans, and the best macaroni and cheese you've ever had!
name: Fathead Bbq Etc
